    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed the required level. The single shortfall (Test conditions, achieved 2 vs. required 3) is acknowledged; however, the remaining factors collectively provide sufficient evidence that the FEA ensemble reliably predicts ASTM F1717 compression-bending behavior for the non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw construct. The overall credibility evidence supports acceptance of the simulation results for the stated COU.",
